in%20the%20past%20after%20helping%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-worker-side-gig-freelance-training-reviewing-ads-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egig%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20answer%20a%20key%20question%3A%20Which%20rides%20and%20deliveries%20make%20the%20most%20financial%20sense%20to%20take%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGigU%20uses%20information%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-grubhub-uber-workers-gig-work-feels-like-a-job-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eindependent%20contractors%3C%2Fa%3E%20see%20on-screen%20when%20they%20are%20offered%20a%20gig%20to%20calculate%20an%20estimate%20of%20how%20much%20the%20worker%20will%20earn%20per%20mile%20and%20at%20an%20hourly%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feature%2C%20which%20GigU%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bcherry%20picker%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20designed%20to%20help%20drivers%20and%20delivery%20workers%20accept%20or%20reject%20a%20job%20within%20the%20seconds-long%20window%20that%20most%20apps%20give%20them%2C%20its%20founders%20say.%20The%20app%20works%20with%20only%20Android%20phones%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20tend%20to%20accept%20it%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Luiz%20Gustavo%20Neves%2C%20GigU's%20CEO%20and%20co-founder%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFactors%20like%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20car%20maintenance%20mean%20that%20gig%20workers%20%26quot%3Bneed%20to%20be%20more%20alert%20to%20which%20rides%20are%20profitable%20and%20which%20ones%20are%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGigU%20is%20one%20of%20multiple%20third-party%20apps%20that%20say%20they%20give%20gig%20workers%20more%20information%20%E2%80%94%20and%20potentially%20help%20them%20earn%20more.%20Many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-lyft-instacart-gig-workers-saw-earnings-fall-2024-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egig%20workers%20saw%20their%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20apps%20like%20Uber%20and%20Instacart%20fall%20in%202024%20despite%20spending%20a%20similar%20or%20greater%20amount%20of%20time%20on%20the%20platforms%2C%20a%20study%20by%20data%20analytics%20company%20Gridwise%20earlier%20this%20year%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20GigU%2C%20users%20can%20set%20specific%20ranges%20for%20pay%20and%2C%20for%20ride-hailing%20gigs%2C%20passenger%20ratings.%20Based%20on%20those%20settings%2C%20GigU%20assigns%20a%20color%20to%20orders%20or%20rides%20as%20they%20pop%20up%20on%20screen%3A%20Green%20for%20a%20job%20that%20would%20be%20the%20most%20lucrative%20for%20the%20driver%2C%20yellow%20for%20options%20with%20earnings%20that%20mostly%20fall%20between%20the%20ranges%20that%20users%20set%2C%20and%20red%20for%20a%20job%20that%20doesn't%20meet%20their%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshots%20show%20how%20GigU%20evaluates%20different%20rides%20on%20Uber.%20One%20on%20the%20far%20left%20shows%20a%20green-coded%20ride%2C%20suggesting%20that%20it%20meets%20the%20driver's%20goals%2C%20one%20in%20the%20middle%20shows%20a%20yellow-coded%20ride%2C%20and%20the%20one%20on%20the%20right%20shows%20a%20red-coded%20ride.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68238ff168a292900801326d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHow%20trips%20on%20Uber%20look%20to%20GigU%20users%3Cp%3EGigU%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concern%20of%20declining%20pay%20was%20one%20reason%20that%20Neves%20and%20Pedro%20Inada%2C%20GigU's%20other%20co-founder%2C%20started%20creating%20businesses%20catered%20to%20gig%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInada%20and%20Neves%20founded%20StopClub%20in%20Brazil%20as%20a%20pit-stop%20where%20gig%20workers%20in%20Brazil%20could%20get%20a%20bite%20to%20eat%20and%20have%20their%20car%20cleaned%2C%20they%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20BI.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20the%20pandemic%20started%2C%20they%20launched%20an%20app%20for%20workers%20who%20couldn't%20gather%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20they%20added%20a%20forerunner%20of%20the%20cherry%20picker%20function%20that%20GigU%20offers.%20The%20idea%20came%20from%20one%20of%20the%20app's%20users%2C%20Inada%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20said%2C%20look%2C%20we%20really%20have%20to%20select%20the%20rides%2C%26quot%3B%20Inada%20said.%20%26quot%3BDriver%20pay%20hasn't%20gone%20up.%20Inflation%20is%20up.%20Could%20you%20guys%20build%20something%20that%20would%20help%20us%20choose%20the%20best%20offers%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGigU%20said%20it%20has%20raised%20about%20%245%20million%20in%20seed%20funding%2C%20part%20of%20which%20will%20bankroll%20its%20US%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGigU%20says%20that%20its%20app%20can%20analyze%20information%20from%20multiple%20gig-work%20apps%2C%20including%20Uber%2C%20Uber%20Eats%2C%20Lyft%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoordash-using-w2-employees-not-gig-workers-make-some-deliveries-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDoorDash%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20GigU%20doesn't%20have%20relationships%20with%20those%20companies%2C%20and%20the%20cofounders%20ended%20up%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20with%20Uber%20in%202023%20over%20the%20similar%20feature%20in%20StopClub's%20app%20in%20Brazil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20Brazil%20said%20that%20the%20app%20violated%20local%20copyright%20and%20competition%20laws%C2%A0and%20illegally%20obtained%20and%20stored%20confidential%20data%20from%20the%20Uber%20app%2C%20tech%20news%20site%20Rest%20of%20World%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frestofworld.org%2F2023%2Fstopclub-app-uber-driver-cost-breakdown%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0at%20the%20time.%20A%20court%20in%20Brazil%20decided%20in%20favor%20of%20GigU%20and%20allowed%20the%20app%20to%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Uber%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Busing%20automation%20tools%2C%20apps%2C%20or%20bots%20to%20manipulate%20the%20Uber%20app%20or%20access%20Uber%20data%20in%20any%20way%20isn't%20allowed%26quot%3B%20per%20its%20community%20guidelines%20and%20terms%20of%20service.%20Uber%20is%20still%20%26quot%3Bengaged%20on%20the%20legal%20front%20in%20Brazil%26quot%3B%20with%20GigU%20and%20StopClub%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoorDash%20and%20Lyft%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGigU's%20founders%20say%20that%20their%20app%20merely%20takes%20information%20that%20the%20gig%20worker%20already%20sees%20and%20presents%20it%20in%20a%20more%20analytical%20context.%20From%20there%2C%20it's%20up%20to%20the%20gig%20worker%20to%20make%20a%20choice%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20doesn't%20accept%20jobs%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20workers%20or%20spoof%20their%20GPS%20location%2C%20Neves%20added.%20Other%20third-party%20apps%2C%20known%20among%20gig%20workers%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-gig-worker-shopper-says-bots-key-to-making-money-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebots%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20are%20capable%20of%20those%20kinds%20of%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20users%20asking%20us%20to%20do%20that%20kind%20of%20stuff%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Neves%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20said%2C%20no%2C%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that%2C%20because%20that%20is%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20give%20them%20transparency%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20that%20transparency%20can%20make%20a%20difference%20for%20gig%20workers%20served%20a%20trip%20or%20order%20while%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20completing%20one%2C%20said%20Len%20Sherman%2C%20an%20executive%20in%20residence%20and%20adjunct%20professor%20at%20Columbia%20Business%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20gig%20worker%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20system%20overload