20and%20potentially%20unethical%20nature%2C%20especially%20for%20young%20job%20seekers%20who%20may%20not%20realize%20they%20are%20not%20talking%20to%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20human%20element%20has%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20process%20somewhere%20along%20the%20line%2C%20in%20DeJeu's%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20I%20am%20going%20to%20make%20lots%20of%20positive%20facial%20expressions%20to%20convince%20this%20AI%20tool%20that%20I'm%20a%20nice%20person%2C%20that's%20just%20so%20weird%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20trying%20to%20convince%20a%20non-human%20entity%20that%20I'm%20a%20smart%2C%20capable%2C%20warm%20human.%20There's%20a%20weirdness%20to%20it%20that%20makes%20me%20uncomfortable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisclosure%20is%20key%2C%20DeJeu%20said%20%E2%80%94%20otherwise%20people%20are%20likely%20to%20feel%20insulted%20when%20they%20expect%20to%20be%20interviewed%20by%20a%20human%20and%20are%20instead%20met%20with%20a%20bot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emily%20DeJeu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681cc8f33fe8d39283654ae1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmily%20DeJeu%20is%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University.%3Cp%3EEmily%20DeJeu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a28832a9-1d05-416f-8251-127a0472ea81%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20prepare%20for%20meeting%20an%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDeJeu's%20advice%20for%20anyone%20who%20knows%20they%20are%20going%20into%20an%20interview%20with%20an%20AI%20is%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bthree%20V's%26quot%3B%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f416a2b-bd29-4304-a3ab-948838373ff0%5C%22%3E1.%20Visuals%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20visuals%20are%20what%20you%20look%20like%2C%20so%20make%20sure%20your%20background%20is%20professional%20and%20you're%20dressed%20as%20you%20would%20be%20in%20any%20other%20interview%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWear%20your%20suit.%20Think%20about%20your%20background%2C%26quot%3B%20DeJeu%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20really%20want%20to%20think%20about%20how%20you%20use%20engaging%20expressions%20with%20your%20face%20and%20how%20you%20bring%20your%20hands%20into%20it.%20It's%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20prep%20that%20I%20would%20give%20if%20you%20were%20going%20to%20give%20a%20presentation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dc9aff74-903f-446a-9d20-6561758f5152%5C%22%3E2.%20Vocals%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20AI%20is%20also%20taking%20note%20of%20your%20vocals%20%E2%80%94%20how%20fast%20you're%20talking%2C%20your%20vocal%20variety%2C%20how%20often%20you%20pause%2C%20and%20if%20you%20use%20a%20lot%20of%20filler%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20you%20practice%20your%20response%20enough%20that%20you%20feel%20really%20fluent%20in%20answering%20and%20you're%20able%20to%20reduce%20your%20filler%20words%3F%26quot%3B%20DeJeu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20backtrack%2C%20sidetrack%2C%20tangential%20statements%20built%20into%20your%20answer.%20You%20can%20speak%20directionally%2C%20answer%20the%20question%20in%20full%2C%20put%20a%20period%20at%20the%20end%20when%20you're%20done%2C%20and%20stop%20talking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220796cd19-819d-44f3-8044-6d6767d8e041%5C%22%3E3.%20Verbals%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20you%20should%20notice%20the%20words%20you're%20using%20and%20the%20sentence%20structures%20you're%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeJeu%20said%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20mine%20job%20ads%20for%20keywords%20and%20make%20sure%20they%20say%20them%20repeatedly%20through%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20that%20a%20human%20recruiter%20would%20be%20kind%20of%20tallying%20in%20their%20minds%2C%20'they%20said%20collaborative%20leadership%20six%20times%2C'%20but%20an%20AI%20tool%20absolutely%20would%20be%20able%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%