%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20social%20media%20posts%20show%20he%20is%20focused%20on%20the%20oil%20market.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Cardy%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20analysts%20scrutinized%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20social%20media%20posts%20for%20oil%20price%20insights.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20said%20Trump's%20posts%20show%20a%20correlation%20with%20oil%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20analysts%20concluded%20that%20the%20president%20prefers%20West%20Texas%20Intermediate%20prices%20in%20the%20%2440-%2450%20a%20barrel%20range.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%3C%2Fa%3E%20social%20media%20posts%20have%20long%20gripped%20global%20markets.%20Now%2C%20even%20Goldman%20Sachs%20commodity%20analysts%20are%20scrutinizing%20them%20for%20clues%20to%20his%20views%20on%20oil%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20analysis%20of%20Trump's%20social%20media%20posts%20on%20Twitter%20and%20Truth%20Social%2C%20Goldman's%20analysts%20concluded%20that%20the%20president%20appears%20to%20favor%20West%20Texas%20Intermediate%20oil%20in%20the%20%2440%20to%20%2450%20barrel%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20wrote%20that%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bpropensity%20to%20post%20about%20oil%20prices%20bottoms%26quot%3B%20when%20prices%20are%20in%20this%20price%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price%3Ftype%3Dwti%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20WTI%20oil%20futures%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20now%20trading%20around%20%2463%20a%20barrel%20%E2%80%94%20well%20above%20Trump's%20apparent%20comfort%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20reviewed%20more%20than%201%2C000%20posts%20from%2016%20years%20to%20identify%20patterns%20in%20Trump's%20thinking%20on%20oil.%20Energy%20market-related%20topics%20accounted%20for%20just%20over%201%25%20of%20Trump's%20social%20media%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20has%20always%20been%20focused%20on%20energy%20markets%2C%20oil%2C%20and%20on%20US%20energy%20dominance%2C%20having%20posted%20nearly%20900%20times%20about%20energy%20markets%20since%20he%20joined%20Twitter%20in%202009%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Goldman%20Sachs'%20analysts%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20energy%20prices%20are%20one%20of%20Trump's%20campaign%20promises%2C%20as%20higher%20oil%20prices%20drive%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Trump%20also%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-drill-baby-drill-agenda-cabinet-picks-oil-gas-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%26quot%3Bdrill%2C%20baby%2C%20drill%26quot%3B%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20agenda%20that%20aims%20to%20boost%20the%20US's%20energy%20dominance%20and%20increase%20the%20country's%20fossil%20fuel%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20tends%20to%20call%20for%20lower%20prices%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20or%20celebrate%20declining%20prices%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhen%20WTI%20prices%20move%20above%20%2450%20a%20barrel%2C%20wrote%20the%20analysts%20at%20Goldman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20has%20called%20for%20higher%20prices%20when%20prices%20are%20very%20low%20(WTI%26lt%3B%2430)%2C%20often%20in%20the%20context%20of%20supporting%20US%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20estimates%20average%20breakeven%20prices%20for%20US%20shale%20producers%20at%20%2451%20a%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trump%20seems%20to%20like%20lower%20prices%20for%20consumers%2C%20he%20likely%20wouldn't%20want%20prices%20so%20low%20that%20they%20hurt%20American%20oil%20producers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20several%20policymakers%20recognize%3Csup%3E%20%3C%2Fsup%3Ethe%20tendency%20for%20US%20oil%20supply%20growth%20to%20slow%20down%20when%20WTI%20prices%20drop%20into%20the%20%2460s%20and%20approach%20the%20breakeven%20price%20of%20numerous%20producers%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20Goldman%20analysts%20expect%20Trump's%20impact%20on%20global%20oil%20production%20to%20be%20limited%20in%20the%20short%20term.%20Furthermore%2C%20US%20regulatory%20easing%20may%20also%20only%20boost%20production%20significantly%20over%20the%20longer%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump's%20inferred%20preference%20for%20relatively%20low%20oil%20prices%20directionally%20supports%20our%20view%20that%20oil%20prices%20are%20likely%20to%20edge%20lower%20in%202025-2026%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20forecast%20the%20WTI%20oil%20price%20to%20average%20%2456%20a%20barrel%20for%20the%20rest%20of%202025%20and%20%2452%20a%20barrel%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-today-trump-tariffs-trade-war-opec-supply-boost-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOil%20prices%20have%20been%20under%20pressure%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%20due%20to%20recession%20fears%2C%20fueled%20by%20Trump's%20trade%20war%20and%20OPEC's%20plans%20to%20boost%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20WTI%20oil%20price%20has%20risen%20around%209%25%20over%20the%20last%20five%20trading%20days%20due%20to%20positive%20sentiment%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-trade-deal-agreement-slash-trump-tariffs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS's%20trade%20deal%20with%20China.%20%3C%2Fa%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20still%20about%2012%25%20lower%20year%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-oil-price-target-forecast-trump-so