e.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20team%20focuses%20on%20the%20entire%20creative%20and%20commercial%20process%3A%20We%20design%20games%2C%20handle%20logistics%2C%20and%20take%20care%20of%20sales%20and%20marketing%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20except%20actual%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20happens%20in%20China%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpandagm.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20Panda%3C%2Fa%3E.%20China%20has%20entire%20industries%20built%20around%20custom%20game%20components%2C%20such%20as%20wooden%20tokens%2C%20custom%20dice%2C%20and%20specialty%20molds.%20The%20US%20doesn't%2C%20and%20those%20components%20are%20expensive%20to%20make%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20games%20are%20made%2C%20about%2065%25%20are%20shipped%20to%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20largely%20go%20to%20Europe%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22245a00df-5748-4585-9832-0e1066865d5b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe're%20the%20ones%20paying%20the%20tariffs%20%E2%80%94%20not%20China%20or%20our%20customers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20already%20started%20a%20large%20print%20run%20of%20250%2C000%20games%20before%20the%20tariffs%20were%20introduced%2C%20none%20of%20which%20have%20sold%20to%20customers%20yet.%20Some%20are%20earmarked%20for%20distributors%2C%20but%20distributors%20pay%20us%20after%20goods%20are%20delivered.%20That's%20part%20of%20what%20made%20this%20so%20difficult%20%E2%80%94%20we'd%20already%20invested%20heavily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20we've%20only%20paid%20around%20%245%2C000%20in%20tariffs%20on%20a%20small%20shipment%20that%20left%20China%20in%20early%20February%2C%20right%20when%20the%20initial%2020%25%20tariff%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20passed%20along%20the%20full%20145%25%20tariff%20to%20customers%2C%20a%20popular%20game%20like%20Wingspan%2C%20which%20sells%20for%20%2465%2C%20would%20suddenly%20cost%20close%20to%20%24200.%20No%20one%20would%20buy%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20we're%20starting%