20to%20quit%20their%20antidepressant%20and%20failed.%20More%20than%2085%25%20of%20their%20patients%20have%20tried%20to%20stop%20once%20before%2C%20and%20more%20than%2060%25%20have%20tried%20to%20stop%20at%20least%20twice%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3Cp%3EOutro%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20Horowitz%20said%2C%20doctors%20had%20been%20taught%20that%20the%20drugs%20are%20effective%2C%20side%20effects%20are%20minimal%2C%20and%20quitting%20takes%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlowly%2C%20that%20framework%20has%20been%20shifting%2C%20with%20the%20recognition%20that%20these%20medications%20are%20not%20a%20one-size-fits-all%2C%20and%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC8841913%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareful%20withdrawal%20schedules%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20needed.%20There's%20been%20a%20growing%20recognition%20that%20something%20called%20%26quot%3Bantidepressant%20continuation%20syndrome%26quot%3B%20is%20real%2C%20and%20may%20impact%20between%2015%25-20%25%20of%20patients%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20stop%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20may%20still%20quibble%20about%20the%20finer%20details%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20but%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0306460318308347%3Fvia%253Dihub%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerally%20agree%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20most%20patients%20trying%20to%20quit%20antidepressants%20will%20experience%20some%20kind%20of%20withdrawal%2C%20whether%20mild%20or%20severe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22outro%20screenshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6823c47c68a2929008013b97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20the%20Outro%20platform.%20The%20company%20says%20its%20monthly%20plans%20will%20cost%20between%20%24125%20and%20%24295.%3Cp%3EOutro%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20he%20is%20based%2C%20Horowitz%20was%20part%20of%20a%20national%20reckoning%20about%20how%20the%20drugs%20are%20used.%20In%20addition%20to%20igniting%20an%20online%20firestorm%20about%20whether%20there's%20really%20a%20%26quot%3Bchemical%20imbalance%26quot%3B%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D8dab63ff6074295b2a892e7b98dc7bad3a3a8090635b12e80caf40a45e8cfac4%26postID%3D6823bab5956ea078b93afe30%26postSlug%3Dhow-to-quit-antidepressants-online-clinic-outro-tapering-microdosing-2025-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs41380-022-01661-0%2523Sec13%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20serotonin%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20corrected%20by%20antidepressants%2C%20he%20published%20a%20widely-cited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F30850328%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2019%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Btapering%20of%20SSRI%20treatment%20to%20mitigate%20withdrawal%20symptoms.%26quot%3B%20The%20study%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20to%20suggest%20that%20tapering%20should%20be%20done%20down%20to%20doses%20much%20lower%20than%20you%20can%20get%20by%20just%20cutting%20up%20pills%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20opened%20a%20deprescribing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nelft.nhs.uk%2Fnational-psychiatric-drug-deprescribing-clinic-pdc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclinic%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20London%2C%20and%20coauthored%20a%20bestselling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D0a3b8525a77f72c06da6c5d8086ec160f27adc58c9c20942654f15a7ccca8985%26postID%3D6823bab5956ea078b93afe30%26postSlug%3Dhow-to-quit-antidepressants-online-clinic-outro-tapering-microdosing-2025-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FMaudsley-Guidelines-prescribing-Prescribing%252Fdp%252F111982298X%252Fref%253Dzg_bs_g_227701_d_sccl_27%252F146-6348275-2444700%253Fpsc%253D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehandbook%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20clinicians%3B%20it's%20the%20Maudsley%20Prescribing%20Guidelines'%20first%20de-prescribing%20reference.%20The%20UK's%20national%20healthcare%20service%20is%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffuturecarecapital.org.uk%2Flatest%2Freducing-antidepressants-through-social-prescribing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eencouraging%3C%2Fa%3E%20doctors%20to%20do%20more%20%26quot%3Bsocial%20prescribing%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20patients%2C%20through%20initiatives%20like%20insomnia%20support%20groups%2C%20art%20and%20music%20classes%2C%20or%20more%20time%20outdoors%20for%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20Horowitz%20says%2C%20the%20overprescription%20problem%20has%20persisted%2C%20with%20many%20patients%20not%20getting%20the%20advice%20they%20need%20to%20properly%20taper.%20Since%20he%20went%20public%20with%20his%20own%20struggles%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%20Horowitz%20says%20he's%20received%20over%2020%2C000%20emails%2C%20%26quot%3Bmostly%20from%20Americans%20asking%20me%20to%20help%20them%20come%20off%20their%20drugs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinsberg%20says%20this%20may%20be%20down%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20US%20has%20a%20more%20decentralized%20healthcare%20system%20than%20the%20UK.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20help%20with%20deprescribing%20is%20highly%20variable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20%E2%80%94%20including%2C%20at%20one%20point%2C%20Horowitz%20himself%20%E2%80%94%20find%20themselves%20digging%20through%20online%20communities%20on%20sites%20like%20Facebook%20or%20Reddit%2C%20looking%20for%20advice%20or%20to%20share%20their%20best%20practices%20for%20how%20to%20come%20off%20these%20medications%20without%20the%20mild%20to%20severe%20insomnia%2C%20anxiety%2C%20panic%2C%20fatigue%2C%20stomach%20problems%2C%20tingly%20fingers%2C%20and%20suicidal%20thoughts%20that%20can%20result%20from%20quitting%20too%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22442c4abd-1195-41ba-953b-e29c7a272aa3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutro's%20equipment%20includes%20oral%20syringes%20and%20compounded%20microdoses.%20Some%20say%20that's%20overkill.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kid%20taking%20oral%20syringe%20medicine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6823c56fc6ad288d1480d9de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOral%20syringes%20are%20common%20in%20pediatrics%2C%20but%20it's%20unusual%20for%20adults%20to%20use%20them.%3Cp%3EKunlathida%20Petchuen%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOutro%20moved%20into%20US%20beta%20mode%20last%20summer.%20Around%20100%20American%20patients%20have%20tried%20out%20the%20service.%20It's%20staffed%20by%20nurse%20practitioners%20and%20psychiatrists%20trained%20in%20Horowitz's%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20patients%20who%20don't%20have%20a%20doctor%20who%20knows%20as%20much%20about%20tapering%2C%20it's%20possible%20Outro%20could%20help%20fill%20a%20gap.%20Outro%20uses%20a%20risk%20calculator%20Horowitz%20developed%20to%20help%20determine%20the%20best%20deprescribing%20schedule%20for%20a%20particular%20patient.%20It%20considers%20factors%20including%20how%20long%20a%20person%20has%20been%20on%20their%20medication(s)%2C%20and%20why.%20The%20program%20is%20designed%20to%20last%20from%20one%20to%20two%20years%2C%20but%20the%20schedule%20can%20vary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20Outro's%20deprescribing%2C%20patients%20have%20regular%20check-ins%20with%20clinicians.%20Some%20gradually%20lower%20their%20dosage%20once%20a%20month%2C%20using%20compounded%20pills%2C%20others%20use%20a%20syringe%20to%20feed%20themselves%20incrementally%20smaller%20and%20smaller%20doses%20of%20their%20drug%2C%20day%20by%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20method%20taps%20into%20patient%20demand%20for%20personalized%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-supplements-live-longer-precision-medicine-doctor-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprecision%20medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20it's%20unclear%20how%20many%20patients%20require%20%E2%80%94%20or%20stand%20to%20benefit%20%E2%80%94%20from%20new%20doses%20that%20aren't%20already%20available%20in%20pharmacies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20does%20not%20accept%20insurance%20(prices%20range%20from%20%24125%20to%20%24295%20per%20month%2C%20not%20including%20the%20compounded%20medicine).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20to%20pay%20cash%20just%20to%20get%20off%20antidepressants%20when%20that%20should%20be%20in%20the%20wheelhouse%20of%20the%20provider%20that%20is%20prescribing%20those%20antidepressants%20is%20problematic%2C%26quot%3B%20Winsberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20the%20problem%20is%20less%20about%20coming%20up%20with%20the%20perfect%20formula%20for%20tapering%2C%20it's%20more%20about%20introducing%20the%20idea%20of%20tapering%20when%20it's%20appropriate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd9f7287-5fc7-4de9-a693-4f6cf310dcbf%5C%22%3EA%20holistic%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20psychiatry%20field%20still%20hasn't%20quite%20cracked%20the%20code%20on%20how%2C%20exactly%2C%20antidepressant%20withdrawal%20syndrome%20manifests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20it's%20more%20common%20in%20female%20patients%2C%20and%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20Outro's%20patients%20are%20women.%20Should%20women%20time%20their%20tapering%20based%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fmenstrual-cycle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20cycle%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Maybe.%20It's%20something%20both%20Outro%20and%20Winsberg%20consider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20more%20to%20learn%20about%20antidepressant%20discontinuation%20syndrome%2C%26quot%3B%20Winsberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BDoes%20it%20mean%20the%20patient%20is%20relapsing%3F%20Does%20it%20mean%20that%20we%20need%20to%20more%20carefully%20perfect%20when%20they're%20coming%20off%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHorowitz%20says%20he%20is%20recruiting%20clinicians%20who%20are%20interested%20in%20exploring%20%26quot%3Blots%20of%20other%20things%20people%20can%20do%20to%20keep%20themselves%20from%20being%20depressed%20and%20anxious%2C%26quot%3B%20besides%20drugs.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20often%20into%20holistic%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20isn't%20just%20a%20woo-woo%20line%20of%20thinking%3A%20there%20is%20hard%20evidence%20suggesting%20that%20things%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeditation-daily-as-effective-as-lexapro-reducing-anxiety-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeditation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20exercise%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apa.org%2Fpubs%2Fhighlights%2Fspotlight%2Fissue-125%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejust%20as%20effective%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20antidepressant%20medication%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20hypothesis%20is%20that%20more%20and%20more%20people%20will%20want%20to%20explore%20getting%20off%20their%20antidepressant%2C%26quot%3B%20Horowitz's%20Outro%20cofounder%2C%20Brandon%20Goode%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BMore%20and%20more%20people%20will%20reconsider%20if%20long-term%20or%20lifelong%20antidepressant%20use%20is%20actually%20right%20for%20them%2C%20because%20they%20will%20have%20a%20fuller%20picture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-quit-antidepressants-online-clinic-outro-tapering-microdosing-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747213261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6823bcb2c6ad288d1480d96d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-quit-antidepressants-online-clinic-outro-tapering-microdosing-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20network%20of%20online%20clinics%20called%20Outro%20aims%20to%20get%20people%20off%20antidepressants%20%E2%80%94%20slowly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrueck%40businessinsider.com%20(Hilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-quit-antidepressants-online-clinic-outro-tapering-microdosing-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20get%20a%20job%20in%20the%20booming%20business%20of%20secondaries%2C%20or%20trading%20shares%20of%20private%20funds.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20collage%20of%20someone%20being%20handed%20cash%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68238b3268a2929008013198%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPrivate%20equity%20secondaries%20have%20gone%20from%20a%20niche%20to%20a%20must-have%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20offers%20maybe%20the%20industry's%20best%20potential%20career%20paths%2C%20with%20open%20space%20for%20more%20partners.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20asked%20investors%20and%20recruiters%20about%20how%20to%20get%20a%20job%20in%20the%20secondaries%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Keith%20Brittain%20was%20starting%20out%2C%20buying%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-secondaries-top-firms-careers-workflow-jobs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20secondhand%20shares%20in%20private%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20considered%20a%20niche%20investment%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20at%20Hamilton%20Lane%20in%202010%20and%20came%20from%2010%20years%20of%20investment%20banking%2C%20and%20until%20I%20started%20talking%20to%20the%20team%20here%20about%20the%20role%2C%20frankly%2C%20back%20then%20I%20didn't%20know%20much%20about%20the%20secondary%20market%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Brittain%2C%20cohead%20of%20Hamilton%20Lane's%20secondary%20business%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20practice%20of%20buying%20stakes%20in%20private%20funds%20from%20investors%20who%20want%20to%20sell%20early%20is%20on%20the%20lips%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20private%20equity%20as%20%26quot%3Bsecondaries%26quot%3B%20fundraising%20reaches%20record%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Michael%20Arougheti%2C%20CEO%20of%20Ares%2C%20secondaries%20%26quot%3Bare%20significant%20beneficiaries%20of%20a%20slowdown%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20economy.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-junior-staff-participate-deal-meetings-top-execs-career-development-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlackstone%20president%20Jon%20Gray%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20secondaries'%20ability%20to%20provide%20liquidity%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20seen%20as%20attractive%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20it%20will%20be%20hard%20to%20exit%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20industry%20evolves%20from%20a%20curiosity%20to%20a%20destination%2C%20a%20lucrative%20career%20path%20is%20emerging.%20We%20spoke%20to%20recruiters%20and%20industry%20experts%20to%20understand%20the%20paths%20to%20a%20career%20in%20secondaries%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20perks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20they%20see%20more%20job%20opportunities%20opening%20up%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapollo-global-1q-earnings-trump-tariffs-buying-opportunity-bonds-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emegafunds%2C%20like%20Apollo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20launch%20inaugural%20funds%2C%20and%20industry%20veterans%20launch%20new%20shops%20%E2%80%94%20as%20Vincent%20Gombault%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Ardian%2C%20did%20with%20Clipway%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOther%20than%20fundraising%2C%20the%20primary%20thing%20that%20could%20hold%20the%20industry%20back%20is%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brittain.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20more%20great%20talent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECandidates%2C%20however%2C%20could%20soon%20see%20more%20competition%20as%20the%20industry's%20reputation%20appears%20to%20be%20luring%20new%20applicants.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20now%20seeing%20interest%20from%20college%20students%20and%20people%20who%20currently%20work%20at%20buyout%20firms%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Matt%20Roche%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20StepStone%2C%20a%20private%20markets%20investor%20with%20%24179%20billion%20in%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20payoff%2C%20he%20added%2C%20could%20be%20big%20for%20those%20who%20make%20it%2C%20including%20an%20improved%20chance%20at%20becoming%20a%20partner%2C%20the%20holy%20grail%20of%20the%20financial%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20the%20most%20pessimistic%20participants%20in%20the%20secondary%20market%20expect%20this%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20growth%20parts%20of%20all%20private%20equity%20and%20just%20alternatives%20generally%2C%26quot%3B%20Roche%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d21b0bc6-45c3-4f97-9286-2c3ed9237f97%5C%22%3EStarting%20your%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20path%20to%20a%20job%20in%20secondaries%20is%20to%20start%20from%20the%20bottom.%20Like%20with%20other%20private%20equity%20jobs%2C%20this%20often%20means%20first%20doing%20a%20stint%20as%20an%20investment%20banking%20analyst%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-recruiting-on-cycle-prepare-career-jamie-dimon-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanks%20are%20a%20common%20hunting%20ground%20for%20private%20equity%20recruiters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20keep%20hearing%20from%20our%20clients%20is%20that%20their%20preferred%20profile%20for%20associate%20hiring%20is%20an%20investment%20banking%20analyst%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20specialty%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alix%20Connors%2C%20Principal%20at%20Opus%20Advisors%2C%20a%20recruiting%20firm%20that's%20long%20recruited%20for%20the%20secondaries%20investors.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20bankers%20with%20active%20deal%20flow%20experience%20and%20strong%20technical%20skills.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoche%20joined%20StepStone%20as%20an%20analyst%20fresh%20out%20of%20undergrad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hire%20analysts%2C%20test%20them%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20and%20then%20keep%20them%20as%20associates%2C%26quot%3B%20Roche%20said.%20Other%20shops%2C%20like%20Hamilton%20Lane%20and%20Blackstone's%20Strategic%20Partners%2C%20also%20hire%20analysts%20out%20of%20college%20into%20their%20secondaries%20businesses%20as%20part%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-blackstone-summer-analyst-program-and-internship-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarger%20analyst%20hiring%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20providing%20an%20even%20more%20direct%20path%20into%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20investment%20banking%20backgrounds%20are%20the%20most%20common%2C%20candidates%20with%20other%20profiles%20have%20broken%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrittain%20said%20that%20people%20who%20have%20worked%20in%20accounting%2C%20corporate%20development%2C%20or%20jobs%20evaluating%20companies%20have%20also%20found%20roles%20as%20secondaries%20investors.%20And%20increasingly%2C%20StepStone%20is%20hiring%20people%20who%20left%20buyout%20roles%20to%20try%20their%20hands%20at%20secondaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211e04dc9-8172-4724-9b71-37c41aece7fd%5C%22%3ESeniors%20and%20specialists%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHilary%20Hurley%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20Amity%20Search%20Partners%2C%20said%20career%20paths%20at%20the%20mid-level%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20typical%20private%20equity%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20either%20did%20junior-level%20banking%20or%20went%20to%20the%20buyout%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Hurley%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20that%20same%20kind%20of%20traditional%20banker%20experience.%26quot%3B'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20formula%20for%20the%20perfect%20candidate%20differs%20depending%20on%20the%20firm%20and%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHurley%20said%20roles%20focused%20on%20deals%20involving%20private%20equity%20firms%20looking%20to%20sell%20a%20portfolio%20company%20to%20a%20new%20fund%20with%20new%20investors%2C%20also%20known%20as%20a%20GP-led%20deal%2C%20will%20%26quot%3Boften%20target%26quot%3B%20candidates%20with%20experience%20as%20direct%20buyout%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20because%20GP-led%20deals%20often%20require%20understanding%20the%20intricacies%20of%20the%20underlying%20assets%20and%20portfolio%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Hurley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20as%20one%20gets%20further%20up%20the%20chain%2C%20having%20real%20secondary%20experience%20becomes%20increasingly%20essential.%20At%20minimum%2C%20you%20will%20need%20solid%20buyout%20investing%20experience%20and%20all%20of%20the%20technical%20skills%20that%20it%20brings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20one%20reason%20many%20of%20the%20largest%20firms%20focus%20on%20promoting%20and%20developing%20in-house%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpportunities%20for%20new%20senior%20roles%20%26quot%3Bcome%20up%20every%20so%20often%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hurley%2C%20such%20as%20when%20a%20new%20firm%20launches%20or%20an%20established%20firm%20launches%20a%20secondaries%20business%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20demand%20for%20the%20secondaries%20market%20has%20also%20increased%20roles%20that%20support%20deal%20flow%2C%20like%20lawyers%2C%20Steven%20Siesser%2C%20chair%20of%20the%20private%20equity%20practice%20and%20cochair%20of%20the%20transactions%20and%20advisory%20practice%2C%20at%20Lowenstein%20Sandler%20LLP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20teams%20that%20do%20nothing%20but%20secondaries%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Siesser%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20transactional%20lawyers%20who%20spend%20their%20days%20buying%20and%20selling%20interests%20in%20GPs%20and%20LPs%2C%20it's%20become%20a%20cottage%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224ba1d619-116f-4547-a5f2-9063bd540a64%5C%22%3ECareer%20considerations%20and%20the%20path%20to%20partner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quality%20of%20candidates%2C%20and%20therefore%20competition%20over%20open%20roles%2C%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCandidates%20seem%20so%20much%20more%20familiar%20with%20secondaries%2C%26quot%3B%20Connors%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20done%20their%20research%20and%20have%20more%20conviction%20in%20this%20asset%20class%20and%20building%20a%20career%20here%20as%20an%20investor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenefits%20tend%20to%20include%20more%20consistent%20hours%2C%20and%20pay%20has%20largely%20caught%20up%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20industry.%20For%20those%20taking%20the%20long%20view%2C%20the%20industry's%20growth%20could%20also%20improve%20one's%20chances%20of%20making%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Brittain%2C%20just%20one%20to%20two%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20value%20of%20the%20private%20investment%20world%20trades%20in%20the%20secondary%20markets%20%E2%80%94%20leaving%20plenty%20of%20room%20for%20growth%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20make%20new%20partners%2C%20they%20need%20to%20have%20a%20reason%20to%20exist%2C%20and%20the%20pie%20has%20to%20grow%20to%20make%20that%20path%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Roche%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20that%20pie%20is%20consistently%20growing%2C%20you%20can%20have%20pieces%20of%20that%20pie%20for%20everyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-secondaries-jobs-career-paths-making-partner-opportunities-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747213201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6823a4af3fe8d3928365bea1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpri